        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer43358040" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5618202763773093334">Oh glorious Eudora! A Southern treasure! Be sure to read about the set of Charles Dickens that her mother scrimped and saved to buy. And how, when the house caught on fire, heck with saving the children, Mama ran upstairs through the smoke and flames to save the books by throwing them out the window to safety...<br/></span>

          </span>
